          "settings": {
            "title": "OUR CRAFTSMANSHIP",
            "size_text": "h2"
          }
        },
        "5b0f48ed-12f4-43e7-a7fd-3e3ea948966e": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "subtext": "Since our journey began, we have been dedicated to delivering excellence in every diamond we create. Rooted in precision and passion, our process blends traditional artistry with modern innovation.\n\nEach diamond is carefully selected, expertly cut, and thoroughly inspected by skilled artisans and gemologists to ensure unmatched brilliance and quality. From sourcing to final finishing, every step is handled with attention to detail and a commitment to perfection.\n\nWe believe in maintaining the highest standards — not just in craftsmanship, but in trust, transparency, and authenticity. Our mission is to bring you diamonds that are not only beautiful, but timeless symbols of elegance and value."
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
