          }
        },
        "8a950665-fd5a-43a3-bf89-8ba1c9967e92": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "subtext": "Our expert team of artisans and gemologists work together with precision and passion to craft diamonds of the highest quality. With years of experience and deep understanding of materials, every piece is designed to achieve perfect balance, brilliance, and elegance.\n\nFrom shaping raw diamonds to refining every detail, our craftsmen ensure flawless execution at every stage. Each diamond is carefully cut, polished, and inspected to meet the highest standards of excellence.\n\nWe believe true beauty lies in precision and consistency, which is why every creation is tested and perfected before reaching you. Our commitment to craftsmanship ensures that every diamond we deliver is timeless, durable, and a true reflection of luxury."
          }
        }
      },
